14:18.066 --> 14:19.476
And / fear...

14:19.818 --> 14:21.228
/ fear what I’m becoming.

14:22.446 --> 14:23.777
Mohinder?

14:52.184 --> 14:53.549
What do you want?

14:53.643 --> 14:55.429
(BREATHING DEEPLY)

14:56.480 --> 14:58.186
I need your help.

14:59.149 --> 15:02.061
I need you to tell me
everything you know
about Sylar.

15:02.194 --> 15:04.651
Sylar?
l have to find him.

15:04.863 --> 15:08.151
He's supposed to help me.

15:08.241 --> 15:12.029
But, why? Why Sylar?

15:13.205 --> 15:15.036
Mohinder, are you okay?
What happened to you?

15:15.207 --> 15:16.572
(GASPING)
What's going on?

15:16.792 --> 15:18.202
Mohinder?

15:21.254 --> 15:25.213
Do not repeat my mistakes.

15:25.300 --> 15:26.710
What happened to you?

15:32.140 --> 15:34.552
MOHINDER: I wanted abilities.

15:34.643 --> 15:38.431
lmpetuous. Selfish.

15:39.147 --> 15:44.437
I got the formula wrong.
So wrong.

15:44.653 --> 15:48.487
Let me help you.
Tell me about Sylar.

15:48.782 --> 15:51.615
Sylar's power is dangerous.

15:51.910 --> 15:53.446
You don't understand it.

15:53.537 --> 15:56.199
I need to understand.
Where is he?

15:57.165 --> 15:58.575
Where is Sylar?

16:00.961 --> 16:04.749
MOHINDER: Costa Verde.
The Bennet house.

16:06.967 --> 16:08.548
Dontgo!

16:29.698 --> 16:33.316
Hey, Uncle Peter.
Dad's making waffles.

16:33.410 --> 16:34.946
(MUS/C PLAYING ON TV)

16:35.036 --> 16:37.368
What's up, champ?
How you doing, man?

16:38.373 --> 16:40.034
Good to see you.

16:40.208 --> 16:41.163
(GRUNTlNG)

16:41.251 --> 16:42.912
Who wants some waffles,
huh?

