18:05.627 --> 18:07.913
You're not from
around here, are you?

18:08.463 --> 18:10.670
No scar.
The past, right?

18:11.258 --> 18:14.591
Which means to you,
I'm the bogeyman.

18:14.678 --> 18:16.088
(CHUCKLES)

18:16.763 --> 18:21.427
It's a hell of a thing,
you coming here to find out
that you and l are brothers.

18:21.518 --> 18:22.633
Brothers?

18:22.769 --> 18:25.636
I'm sorry that you've
come all this way, Peter,
but I can't help you.

18:25.730 --> 18:27.345
Can't?

18:27.649 --> 18:28.855
Won't.

18:28.942 --> 18:30.557
VVhy?

18:31.194 --> 18:33.606
I'm not gonna give it
to you, my ability.
I'm not.

18:33.697 --> 18:36.564
Then I'll just take
what I need from you.

18:36.658 --> 18:38.899
As if you could.

18:43.665 --> 18:47.249
Peter is dead.
They killed him.
And now they are after me.

18:47.335 --> 18:50.543
I am not leaving
without your abilities,
Sylar.

18:54.259 --> 18:56.215
My name is Gabriel.

18:57.554 --> 19:01.513
And you don't realize
my ability is not just
understanding how things work,

19:01.599 --> 19:06.093
there's a hunger that
comes with it.
To know more, to have more,

19:06.187 --> 19:09.645
I couldn't control it
and it turned me
into a killer.

19:10.066 --> 19:11.442
A monster.

19:13.403 --> 19:16.065
And every day is
a struggle, every hour.

19:16.239 --> 19:19.356
But I fight it for him.

19:20.410 --> 19:23.698
And lam not going
to willingly
condemn you to hell.

19:23.788 --> 19:27.747
lfl have your ability,
